samples.conclusion: Evaporator pressure transducer is reading 5.5 psi low. Chiller is running short of refrigerant charge. Chiller is running low condenser water flow.
samples.action: Evaporator pressure transducer needs to be replaced. Need leak repair and refrigerant charge trimmed. Need to look at BAS and figure out condenser pump control, to establish proper water flow.

verified.comment: Evaporator pressure transducer is reading 5.5 psi low. Chiller is running short of refrigerant charge. Chiller is running low condenser water flow. Evaporator pressure transducer needs to be replaced. Need leak repair and refrigerant charge trimmed

samples.conclusion: Chiller running low condenser water flow. Chiller has high start count for run hours. Chiller is not targeting condenser liquid level.
samples.action: Need to verify BAS control of condenser water pump speed. Need to tune the liquid line valve control, this will help prevent surging and reduce the chiller over shooting the chilled water set point and cycling to reduce the number of starts.

verified.comment: Chiller running low condenser water flow. Chiller has high start count for run hours. Chiller is not targeting condenser liquid level. Need to verify BAS control of condenser water pump speed. Need to tune the liquid line valve control

samples.action: Check BAS control or chilled water pump VFD to maintain design flow.
samples.conclusion: Chiller is running low chilled water flow. Also there is no AHU's on so there is no load. Need to re-log the chiller under a load.

verified.comment: Chiller is running low chilled water flow. Also there is no AHU's on so there is no load. Need to re-log the chiller under a load.
